Package oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.dt.common.dtlayout

Interface Summary
ApplcoreButtonListener Interface used for the callback from Applcore Button dtlayout components.
 

Class Summary
ApplcoreCheckBox Provides a label and checkbox.
ApplcoreComboBox Provides a label and a comboBox.
ApplcoreDialog Provides a JEWT dialog configured for use.
ApplcoreEditableTable Provides an editable table with list based data model.
ApplcoreLabel Provides a label.
ApplcoreListItemComboBox  
ApplcoreSelectionTable A table that provides a radio button column to indicate selected row.

ApplcoreTextfield Provides a label and an input textfield.
ApplcoreTextfieldButton Provides a label, an input textfield and a linked button whose action result will update the textfield.
